{
  "stem": "11882.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "[CHUCKLES] But at any rate, this was, for Fraulein Annie, very difficult because little Annamarie, she had to tell her, now, you must go with your father.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Every day, the family-- at least Fraulein Annie and little Ana Marie, and if I were-- while I was there, I went with them-- went to the mother's grave and said a prayer.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "The mother's grave was in a beautiful grave there called the Cavalierberg.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Probably still there, the Cavalierberg.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "But without Herr Sachs, because of course he didn't get buried.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "But at any rate, Herr Sachs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I left.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I left because the school now had many, many students.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And they said, come back, or you'll lose their job.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "It was a threat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "They would have taken me back anyway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "But I quickly went back to my weekly pay.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "Herr Sachs had not had the courage to give me any money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "They gave me nice presents, and I was taken care of there, and I was learning German.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "It was worth my while since I-- the school was in such a dark situation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "But I now had the chance to go back to school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "Come right back, or we can't keep your job for you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "So I went right back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And they went to Berlin with me and bought me a pretty coat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "That was all they could do because his bank was so carefully watched.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And a Jewish man, which they regarded him, was not allowed to give money to anyone.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "You know, it was his money, but at any rate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "Anyhow, that's how it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "They went together with me to Berlin, partway to Hamburg, on my way back to school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And we had a very nice time there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And they brought me this nice coat, the three of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
